name: Invesco S&P/TSX Composite ESG Tilt Index ETF
longDescription: Invesco S&P/TSX Composite ESG Tilt Index ETF the ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible. The Fund before fees and expenses, the performance of the S&P/TSX Composite ESG Tilted Index the underlying index, or any successor thereto. This Invesco ETF invests, directly or indirectly, primarily in equity securities of companies listed in Canada.
